sub_title: LION - 3000+ add me by invitation to john.grant.at@gmail.com
summary:
30 years of experience in information technology, management consulting, communications, vision/mission development and strategic planning. He has worked in a variety of marketing organizations and with many of the world's great brands.

John’s gifts and talents are in the areas of IT, vision/mission development, strategic planning, marketing, branding, customer experience management, time management/business efficiency, message development and analysis of marketing program effectiveness and efficiency.

Specialties: Assist entrepreneurs of private and publicly-traded SMBs maximize their business’ potential by aligning people, processes, assets & technology behind a competitive business model. Implement results-based changes from the methodical findings of comprehensive analysis designed to identify existing horizontal & vertical disconnects.
